  <refnamediv>
    <refname>avicloseall</refname>
    <refpurpose>Close all opened video files/cameras.</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>


<refsynopsisdiv>
   <title>Syntax</title>
   <synopsis>
   avicloseall()
   
   </synopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsection>
   <title>Description</title>
   <para>
avicloseall close all opened video files or cameras.
   </para>
   <para>
Video support for IPCV is only available when IPCV is compiled with OpenCV which support video I/O.
   </para>
   <para>
</para>
</refsection>

<refsection>
   <title>Examples</title>
   <programlisting role="example"><![CDATA[
n = aviopen(fullpath(getIPCVpath() + "/images/video.avi"));
im = avireadframe(n); //get a frame
imshow(im);
avicloseall;

   ]]></programlisting>
</refsection>

